<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>OOW 60-Day Pre-Expiration Sequence — HBS Training</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0a2a4a;
    --blue: #1a7ab5;
    --blue-light: #4fa3d4;
    --gold: #c9922a;
    --gold-light: #f0c060;
    --cream: #f8f5f0;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --gray-100: #f4f6f8;
    --gray-200: #e8ecf0;
    --gray-400: #9aa5b4;
    --gray-600: #4a5568;
    --gray-800: #1a202c;
    --green: #1d9e75;
    --red: #e24b4a;
    --amber: #ef9f27;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--gray-800);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* TOP BAR */
  .topbar {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 10px 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .topbar img { height: 36px; }
  .topbar-right { font-size: 12px; color: #7eb8d4; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0f3d6b 60%, #1a5a90 100%);
    padding: 80px 48px 72px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -80px; right: -80px;
    width: 400px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26,122,181,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -60px; left: 200px;
    width: 300px; height: 300px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,146,42,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(201,146,42,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,146,42,0.4);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 44px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 680px;
  }
  .hero h1 span { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .hero-stat { }
  .hero-stat-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .hero-stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* MAIN CONTENT */
  .content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 48px 80px;
  }

  /* SECTION HEADERS */
  .section-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .section-divider {
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* OVERVIEW BOX */
  .overview-box {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px 36px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(10,42,74,0.08);
  }
  .overview-box p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .overview-box p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* PURPOSE BOX */
  .purpose-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .purpose-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(10,42,74,0.06);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--blue);
  }
  .purpose-card.gold { border-top-color: var(--gold); }
  .purpose-card.green { border-top-color: var(--green); }
  .purpose-card.amber { border-top-color: var(--amber); }
  .purpose-card-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .purpose-card-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .purpose-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* TIMELINE */
  .timeline { margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .timeline-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    min-width: 48px;
  }
  .timeline-dot {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--navy);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .timeline-dot.blue { background: var(--blue); }
  .timeline-dot.gold { background: var(--gold); }
  .timeline-dot.green { background: var(--green); }
  .timeline-dot.red { background: var(--red); }
  .timeline-dot.gray { background: var(--gray-400); }
  .timeline-line {
    width: 2px;
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--gray-200);
    margin: 4px 0;
    min-height: 24px;
  }
  .timeline-content {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(10,42,74,0.05);
    flex: 1;
  }
  .timeline-day {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .timeline-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .timeline-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .timeline-desc:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .sms-bubble {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--blue);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .branch-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .branch-card {
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .branch-reply { background: #e8f5ee; border-left: 3px solid var(--green); color: #1a5c3a; }
  .branch-timeout { background: #fff3e0; border-left: 3px solid var(--amber); color: #7a4a00; }
  .branch-label { font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; display: block; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }

  /* PIPELINE STAGES */
  .pipeline-track {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(10,42,74,0.06);
  }
  .pipeline-stages {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .stage-pill {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--gray-100);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .stage-pill .dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--blue);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .stage-pill.active { background: #e8f2fb; color: var(--navy); }
  .stage-pill.active .dot { background: var(--blue); }
  .stage-pill.engaged { background: #e8f5ee; color: #1a5c3a; }
  .stage-pill.engaged .dot { background: var(--green); }
  .stage-pill.no-response { background: #fafafa; color: var(--gray-400); }
  .stage-pill.no-response .dot { background: var(--gray-400); }

  /* TAGS */
  .tags-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .tag-badge {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #e6f1fb;
    color: #0c447c;
    border: 1px solid #b8d4f0;
  }

  /* SETEISHA ROLE */
  .role-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a2a4a 0%, #0f3d6b 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 36px 40px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .role-box .section-label { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .role-box .section-title { color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .role-list { list-style: none; }
  .role-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .role-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .role-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* RESPONSE STANDARDS */
  .standards-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(10,42,74,0.06);
  }
  .standards-table th {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .standards-table td {
    padding: 14px 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
  }
  .standards-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .standards-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: var(--gray-100); }
  .standard-time {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  /* CALLOUT */
  .callout {
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .callout-info { background: #e8f2fb; border-left: 4px solid var(--blue); }
  .callout-warning { background: #fff8e6; border-left: 4px solid var(--amber); }
  .callout-success { background: #e8f5ee; border-left: 4px solid var(--green); }
  .callout-icon { font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .callout-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.7; }
  .callout-text strong { color: var(--navy); }

  /* CHECKLIST */
  .checklist {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(10,42,74,0.06);
  }
  .checklist-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .checklist-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .check-box {
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    border: 2px solid var(--gray-200);
    border-radius: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 32px 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .footer-left { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  .footer-right { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }

  /* SECTION SPACING */
  .section { margin-bottom: 56px; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .content { padding: 40px 24px; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 32px; }
    .hero-stats { gap: 24px; }
    .purpose-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .branch-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .topbar { padding: 10px 24px; }
    .footer { padding: 24px; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOP BAR -->
<div class="topbar">
  <img src="https://assets.cdn.filesafe.space/UDKdmJIdT4xB1V6Lye64/media/68f7cb4d3a4642fd12cdeaab.png" alt="Hearing Benefit Services">
  <span class="topbar-right">Staff Training · Confidential</span>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">OOW Campaign · Module 1 of 7</div>
  <h1>OOW 60-Day <span>Pre-Expiration</span> Sequence</h1>
  <p class="hero-subtitle">A complete guide for Seteisha on how the 60-Day Out of Warranty sequence works, what triggers it, and what your role is when a patient engages.</p>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="hero-stat-num">~14</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-label">Days Active</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="hero-stat-num">3</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-label">Touchpoints</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="hero-stat-num">60</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-label">Days Before Expiry</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
<div class="content">

  <!-- OVERVIEW -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Overview</div>
    <div class="section-title">What Is This Campaign?</div>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <div class="overview-box">
      <p>The <strong>60-Day Pre-Expiration Sequence</strong> automatically reaches out to HBS patients whose hearing aids are 60 days away from their warranty expiration date. The goal is to get ahead of the expiration — reaching patients while they still have coverage and time to make a decision.</p>
      <p>The campaign runs entirely on autopilot in GHL. It sends an SMS on Day 1, follows up with an email on Day 2 (if no reply), and includes a call task for Seteisha on Day 4. A final SMS goes out on Day 7. If there is still no response after all touchpoints, the contact moves to the <strong>Contacted – No Response</strong> stage.</p>
      <p>When a patient replies at any point, GHL stops the automated sequence, notifies Seteisha immediately, and moves the contact to the <strong>Engaged (Conversation Started)</strong> stage for human follow-up.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="purpose-grid">
      <div class="purpose-card">
        <div class="purpose-card-icon">⏰</div>
        <div class="purpose-card-title">Proactive Timing</div>
        <p>60 days is the ideal window — patients still have coverage but are close enough to the expiration that the message feels relevant and timely.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="purpose-card gold">
        <div class="purpose-card-icon">🎯</div>
        <div class="purpose-card-title">Highest-Intent Audience</div>
        <p>These are existing patients who already know and trust HBS. They convert at a significantly higher rate than cold leads.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="purpose-card green">
        <div class="purpose-card-icon">🤖</div>
        <div class="purpose-card-title">Fully Automated</div>
        <p>GHL handles all outreach automatically. Seteisha only steps in when a patient replies or when a call task is assigned.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="purpose-card amber">
        <div class="purpose-card-icon">📋</div>
        <div class="purpose-card-title">3 Revenue Paths</div>
        <p>Every patient routes to one of three outcomes: upgrade to new hearing aids, warranty extension, or device repair — each with its own follow-up path.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHAT TRIGGERS IT -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Trigger</div>
    <div class="section-title">What Starts This Workflow?</div>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <div class="callout callout-info">
      <div class="callout-icon">ℹ️</div>
      <div class="callout-text"><strong>Trigger:</strong> The contact tag <code style="background:#d4e9f7;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;">OOW_60</code> is added to a patient's contact record in GHL. This tag is added by Seteisha manually when she confirms through the Signia portal that a patient's warranty expires in approximately 60 days.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="callout callout-warning">
      <div class="callout-icon">⚠️</div>
      <div class="callout-text"><strong>Important:</strong> Once the tag is added, the workflow fires automatically. Double-check the patient's name and contact details before tagging to avoid sending messages to the wrong person.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TIMELINE -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Sequence Flow</div>
    <div class="section-title">Step-by-Step Breakdown</div>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <div class="timeline">

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-left">
          <div class="timeline-dot blue">1</div>
          <div class="timeline-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-day">Immediately on tag</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Day 1 SMS — First Outreach</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">GHL automatically creates an opportunity in the <strong>Out of Warranty Lifecycle</strong> pipeline and sends the first SMS to the patient.</p>
          <div class="sms-bubble">"Hi [First Name], this is Hearing Benefit Services. Your hearing aids may be approaching the end of their warranty period. How have they been performing lately? We'd love to help make sure you're covered. Reply STOP to opt out."</div>
          <div class="branch-grid">
            <div class="branch-card branch-reply">
              <span class="branch-label">✓ If patient replies</span>
              Auto-reply sent → OOW_ENGAGED tag added → Seteisha notified → Move to Engaged stage
            </div>
            <div class="branch-card branch-timeout">
              <span class="branch-label">⏱ If no reply (2 days)</span>
              Continue to Day 2 Email
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-left">
          <div class="timeline-dot blue">2</div>
          <div class="timeline-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-day">Day 2 — If no reply to SMS</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Email Follow-Up — Quick Check</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">GHL sends the <strong>"Quick check on your hearing aids"</strong> email. This is the branded HBS email template with the booking link and three options — performance check, warranty extension, or upgrade review.</p>
          <div class="branch-grid">
            <div class="branch-card branch-reply">
              <span class="branch-label">✓ If patient replies</span>
              Auto-reply sent → OOW_ENGAGED tag → Seteisha notified → Engaged stage
            </div>
            <div class="branch-card branch-timeout">
              <span class="branch-label">⏱ If no reply (2 days)</span>
              Seteisha receives a call task
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-left">
          <div class="timeline-dot gold">3</div>
          <div class="timeline-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-day">Day 4 — If still no reply</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Call Task Assigned to Seteisha</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">GHL creates a task in your task list: <em>"Call [Patient Name] — OOW 60-Day Follow Up"</em>. The task is due the same day at 4:00 PM. This is your cue to pick up the phone.</p>
          <div class="callout callout-success" style="margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:0;">
            <div class="callout-icon">📞</div>
            <div class="callout-text"><strong>Your call goal:</strong> Find out how their hearing aids are performing, mention that their warranty is approaching expiration, and offer to help them explore their options — upgrade, extension, or check-in.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-left">
          <div class="timeline-dot blue">4</div>
          <div class="timeline-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-day">Day 7 — If still no reply</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Final SMS — Soft Follow-Up</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">GHL sends one final SMS before the sequence ends.</p>
          <div class="sms-bubble">"Hi [First Name], just following up — many of our patients at this stage choose to either extend their coverage or explore newer hearing aid options. Happy to walk you through both if helpful. Reply STOP to opt out."</div>
